Author:
Vol / Page:  271/3/2
Edition:
Quote:  The unspeakable dens kept by Marie Vernon and Cecilia Rea in College-street(?) naturally attracted the attention of the police. The Mt. Cook officers were always on the alert, and, though powerless of take any action, the women were given the `chat,' and their business was conducted as privately as possible.
